---
import DraftLayout from '../../layouts/DraftLayout.astro';
---
<DraftLayout title="About Kaja — Subtle Somatics" description="Kaja Possert-Bienzle: somatic practitioner, unfolding companion, integration facilitator. Vienna, Austria." activeNav="about">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">Steady presence, pure unfolding</h1>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="100">My name means <em>solid rock</em> in Turkish and <em>pureness</em> in Swedish — qualities that guide my way of accompanying others.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro quote -->
  <section class="intro-quote-section">
    <div class="intro-quote reveal">
      <p class="gradient-text">"I feel excited to share more of who I am and what is important to me."</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="content-split">
      <div class="content-image reveal-left">
        <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
      </div>
      <div class="content-text reveal-right">
        <h2>Hi, I'm Kaja.</h2>
        <p>I believe that within every person lies a vast treasure of innate resources — strength, love, radiance, trust and peace. These qualities are not something to be acquired from outside, but something to be discovered, remembered and embodied from within.</p>
        <p>What I deeply value about myself is my sincere, deep caring and my finely-tuned attunement that accompanies nourishment, healing and unfolding. I see and mirror qualities of resourcefulness in others — and I feel deeply honoured and blessed to offer Spinal Energetics and presence-based coaching.</p>
        <p>My approach draws from the wisdom of the body-mind-soul system and works with the natural intelligence that already knows how to heal, integrate and align. Through gentle presence and deep listening, we create the conditions for what is most alive and true in you to come forward.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What does subtle mean? -->
  <section class="why-subtle-about">
    <div class="why-subtle-inner reveal">
      <h2 class="text-center">What does <em>subtle</em> mean?</h2>
      <p class="why-subtle-text">Everything starts in a subtle way — even the biggest change and the biggest emotion. There has always been a subtle point before where it started: some heat in the belly, some tingling in the hands. Tuning into the subtle sense when it first appears, there is so much power and clarity and goodness that can be unraveled and unfolded through staying with these subtle senses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visioncasting -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <div class="vision-content text-center reveal">
        <h2>My vision</h2>
        <p>Kaja invites a space where unfolding, presence and deep self-contact can happen naturally. Her work unites energetic, somatic and intuitive methods that support people in connecting with their inner resources, gently dissolving blockages, and finding <em>immediate access to their wholeness</em>.</p>
        <p>In this protected space, processes may unfold — with the invitation to sense what is already there and how it moves or rests.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Approach -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="approach-section reveal">
      <h2 class="text-center">My Approach</h2>
      <p class="approach-text">I combine depth coaching with somatic energetic practices, guided by the principle that your body is wise and your unfolding is trustworthy. My role is to accompany you with steadiness, clarity, and loving attunement. Together, we open a field of presence where transformation arises naturally.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Archetypes -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <div class="archetype-grid">
        <div class="archetype reveal-left">
          <h3>The Space-Opener</h3>
          <p>Kaja does not direct, but accompanies. She widens a space that already exists — a space where people remember their own capacity to heal themselves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="archetype reveal-right">
          <h3>The Gardener & the Gondolier</h3>
          <p>She nurtures what wants to grow and unfold, with patience, mindfulness and trust in the natural process. At the same time, she navigates her clients through profound inner landscapes — not as one who steers, but as a gentle companion on a journey that happens by itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Background Timeline -->
  <section class="section-warm">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">Background & Training</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-left reveal-left">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">Foundation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Education & Anthropology</h4>
            <p>Bachelor of Education + Bachelor of Arts in Anthropology — laying the groundwork for understanding human experience in all its dimensions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-right reveal-right" data-delay="100">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">Facilitation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Teaching & Facilitation</h4>
            <p>Youth education, team building, mindfulness and leadership trainings — learning the art of holding space for others.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-left reveal-left" data-delay="200">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">2022</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Relational Practice</h4>
            <p>Facilitating We-Spaces and Authentic Relating since 2022 — deepening into the relational field.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-right reveal-right" data-delay="300">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">Embodiment</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Yoga & Energy Work</h4>
            <p>200h Yoga Teacher Training in India, Reiki Level I + II — the body as gateway to deeper knowing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-left reveal-left" data-delay="400">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">Service</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Professional Highlights</h4>
            <p>Women's leadership trainings for the UN, retreat facilitation, somatic imaginal inner journeys.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-right reveal-right" data-delay="500">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-year">Now</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>Coaching & Psychotherapy</h4>
            <p>Advanced Coaching Training (Aletheia), ongoing MSc in Integrative Psychotherapy — continuing to deepen.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center reveal" data-delay="200" style="margin:3rem auto 0;color:var(--text-secondary);max-width:650px;">Through these diverse pathways, my devotion remains the same: to accompany others into their innate wholeness and resourcefulness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">Core Principles</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value card-shine reveal" data-delay="0">
        <h3>Presence</h3>
        <p>Being fully here — with what is. Not fixing, not striving, but meeting the moment with open awareness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value card-shine reveal" data-delay="100">
        <h3>Wholeness</h3>
        <p>Recognising that you are already whole. Our work is about removing the layers that obscure this truth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value card-shine reveal" data-delay="200">
        <h3>Embodiment</h3>
        <p>Living from the body's wisdom, not just the mind's understanding. True knowing happens in the tissues, the breath, the bones.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value card-shine reveal" data-delay="300">
        <h3>Trust</h3>
        <p>Trusting the rhythm of your own unfolding. There is an intelligence at work in you that knows the way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Poetic break -->
  <section class="poetic-break">
    <blockquote class="reveal">
      <p class="gradient-text">This is the work of becoming intimate with nuance: reading the breath behind the breath, the movement beneath stillness, the sound inside silence.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <section class="section text-center">
    <h2 class="reveal">I'd love to meet you</h2>
    <p class="reveal" data-delay="100" style="margin:1rem auto 2rem;color:var(--text-secondary);">I'd love to have you and feel honoured to serve you — just where you are.</p>
    <a href="/draft/#contact" class="btn btn-filled reveal" data-delay="200">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>

</DraftLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-hero em { color: var(--accent); }
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }

  /* Intro quote */
  .intro-quote-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--bg-deep);
  }
  .intro-quote { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .intro-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .content-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .content-image img { border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .content-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .content-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  /* What does subtle mean */
  .why-subtle-about {
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .why-subtle-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .why-subtle-inner h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .why-subtle-inner em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .why-subtle-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: none;
  }

  /* Approach */
  .approach-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .approach-section h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .approach-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .vision-content { max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .vision-content h2 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .vision-content p { margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .vision-content em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }

  .archetype-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .archetype { padding: 2rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--accent); }
  .archetype h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .archetype p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.25;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .timeline-marker {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    width: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .timeline-marker::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .timeline-year {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    position: absolute;
    top: -1.4rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .timeline-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(196, 164, 108, 0.02);
  }
  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .timeline-content p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .timeline-left .timeline-content { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1; }
  .timeline-left .timeline-marker { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
  .timeline-left::after { content: ''; grid-column: 3; }

  .timeline-right::before { content: ''; grid-column: 1; }
  .timeline-right .timeline-marker { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
  .timeline-right .timeline-content { grid-column: 3; grid-row: 1; }

  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .value { padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .value h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .value p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .poetic-break { padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: var(--bg-warm); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .poetic-break blockquote { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .poetic-break p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .content-image { max-width: 320px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .archetype-grid, .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .timeline::before { left: 1rem; }
    .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; }
    .timeline-marker { width: 40px; }
    .timeline-left .timeline-content,
    .timeline-right .timeline-content { grid-column: 2; }
    .timeline-left .timeline-marker,
    .timeline-right .timeline-marker { grid-column: 1; }
    .timeline-left::after,
    .timeline-right::before { display: none; }
  }
</style>
